text:
LITTLE VIXEN: Jesy Nelson certainly turned up the BRITs heat 
The X Factor bombshells hit the showbiz bash in a number of jaw-dropping ensembles. 
And Jesy Nelson certainly stood out as she flashed major cleavage. 
As we've all learned by now, when it comes to fashion, Little Mix mean business. The hottest outfits from the BRIT Awards 2017 Wednesday, 22nd February 2017 Take a look at the hottest dresses on the red carpet 1 / 13 
Mike Marsland/WireImage BRIT AWARDS 2017: Little Mix are nominated for an award 
Rocking up to the event in a skintight dress, the Little Mixer went hell for leather.Her smokin' hot outfit featured a belt detail, as well as extra white buttons which drew yet more attention to her chest. 
Although, we're surprised the Essex beauty didn't burst out from her super tight ensemble, as her boobs looked ready to break free from the clutches of the dress. 
Strutting her stuff down the red carpet, Jesy posed up a storm. The hottest photos of Jesy Nelson Sunday, 12th February 2017 Little Mix star Jesy Nelson flaunts her curves in these seriously sexy images. 1 / 30 Jesy shows off her figure in underwear 
GETTY LITTLE MIX BABES: Jesy, Jade, Perrie and Leigh-Anne looked incredible 
The glamorous Shout Out To My Ex songstress wore her long chestnut locks down in loose waves to complete the look. 
Meanwhile, bandmate Jade Thirlwall struggled with her own dress, as she tried not to flash her nether regions. 
However, it all became too much and Jade exposed her knickers in a wardrobe malfunction . The biggest boobs in showbiz Tuesday, 29th November 2016 We take a look at the most impressive cleavage in showbiz 1 / 66 CBB star Chloe Khan flaunts her eye-popping cleavage in skintight dress in London 
PA DARING TO BARE: Jade Thirlwall exposed her knickers 
Jesy and Jade were of course joined by Leigh-Anne Pinnock, and blonde beauty Perrie Edwards. 
It wasn't just Jade to suffer a fashion faux pas.
